k due to an accident. This is the first time I've noticed any sort of weight loss, and I think it's the only thing that could have tipped me off that any weight was being lost as we don't own a scale.

 Before this, I wasn't really active, and I half-heartedly set an unrealistic goal of 10,000 steps a day to try to get me to try to achieve it. I think i achieved it twice in the 4 years since i set that goal. Along with biking 5 days a week and me working at a warehouse store, I'm now reaching that target almost daily that I work. 

It's an electric bike, it does most of the work, but it's working. It's only 4 miles there and back, but it's working. Losing weight wasn't an intention of getting a bike, it was only to be able to get to work and home reliably.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/bB3SQWu</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[whybother]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>MAN!!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/I9zGIWS</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/AYSCQYC.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/I9zGIWS</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[HolyAaron]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Tele-beans</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/gIWWUaN</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/uYnproS.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Sound</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/gIWWUaN</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[neuralous]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Time for the unhinged XL Sunday CeleryDump for the good &amp; bad people of Imgur</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/TJLKiIU</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/z74R1La.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>greeting online friends</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/MXsnm8p.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5RgNrw1.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/uhYum1p.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>seems a tad excessive</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tmsokIn.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/BDRyZJ1.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></